Summary: Context menu on Ctrl+right-click
Class: wish
Priority: low
Difficulty: fun
Fixed-in: 2003-11-20

In Windows PuTTY, a context menu which appears when holding down Ctrl
and right-clicking on the PuTTY window, like in xterm/pterm.

Contains all the System menu options (except move/resize/etc), and
`Paste'.
